{"id": 1010, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都见过哪些无用的远见？", "description": "八字还没一撇，心中已经数到九。（题图来自：Marilyn Faucher）", "record_count": 4646, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703181351L0DTBpIegbolyHV7.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-06-26T01:00:06Z", "options": [{"id": 92928, "content": "我明天一定好好努力把某件事做完。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 290659}, {"id": 93184, "content": "明天开始一定好好学习……", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 565186}, {"id": 92929, "content": "哈哈哈哈，说还是不说呢？", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182923c5JEyLNHfVYnI2O8.jpg", "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 657349}, {"id": 93185, "content": "135 0934 2686 讲带给我好运！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 652025}, {"id": 93186, "content": "等我毕业了。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 565186}, {"id": 93698, "content": "从明天开始.....", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 632962}, {"id": 93187, "content": "妹纸说要跟我天长地久，好烦。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 658311}, {"id": 93188, "content": "制定了满满的健身计划 发誓一定要减肥 然而还是继续肥着", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166776}, {"id": 92933, "content": "每天一定学习一小时，不能再浪了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 105981}, {"id": 93189, "content": "去国外学什么专业", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 652169}, {"id": 92934, "content": "我是喜欢男的好还是喜欢女的好…………结果一个也不喜欢，我还是等着伺候未来我家喵皇好了", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 298191}, {"id": 93446, "content": "和初恋在一起后，是要几个小孩？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 659366}, {"id": 92935, "content": "我以后一定要开一家属于自己的店，各种都设想好了，只差……", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 657725}, {"id": 93191, "content": "这道题等一下在做", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 657849}, {"id": 92936, "content": "等我头发多了点，我要…", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 641744}, {"id": 93192, "content": "写个计划……执行计划……修改计划……撕毁计划，所以没有远见", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 566520}, {"id": 93193, "content": "有钱了就什么都不干了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 649700}, {"id": 92938, "content": "书读得少还想太多", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 657631}, {"id": 93194, "content": "看完这个帖子就睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 658326}, {"id": 94218, "content": "之后要不要考雅思 要不要出国留学", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 663214}, {"id": 92939, "content": "各种鸡汤", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 112082}, {"id": 94987, "content": "明天一定起床吃早餐……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 653303}, {"id": 104203, "content": "等我生了孩子，我一定要……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 700756}, {"id": 92940, "content": "等我赚到多少钱以后", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 639842}, {"id": 92941, "content": "等我有钱了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 112082}, {"id": 93197, "content": "前两天谈一男朋友，刚开始就想着以后在那住，养只什么狗，谁洗衣服谁做饭然而半个月就分手了。宝宝心里苦", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 658337}, {"id": 92943, "content": "买吧等我瘦了以后穿起来一定很好看", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 657729}, {"id": 93199, "content": "等我有钱了。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 652368}, {"id": 92944, "content": "永远不能静下心来学习，精力永远只用了十几分之一", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 655944}, {"id": 93200, "content": "刚刚在一起就开始给未来的孩子起名字。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1127037}, {"id": 92945, "content": "想到自己目前的状态 和以后自己想要的生活  却停滞不前", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 655707}, {"id": 132882, "content": "相爱的人不能在一起", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 830096}, {"id": 92947, "content": "这个东西要留着，以后可能会用到。", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 589811}, {"id": 93203, "content": "如何学习架子鼓", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 658302}, {"id": 95763, "content": "还没承认是男友 都想着生孩子了.", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 663476}, {"id": 92948, "content": "假如我能在deadline前一天做完……", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 499951}, {"id": 92949, "content": "大学里面要不要谈恋爱～", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 657744}, {"id": 93205, "content": "中将怎么去领呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 658358}, {"id": 97557, "content": "晚上12点之前睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 670887}, {"id": 92950, "content": "～", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 657744}, {"id": 93206, "content": "我们以后会好好的，但已经不联系了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 658362}, {"id": 92951, "content": "高数可以最后一天再补的", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 657746}, {"id": 93207, "content": "我一定要好好学习.不玩手机.", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 658371}, {"id": 93463, "content": "那些路上放钉子的人", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182958oHDyhFzLGKlmMgV1.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 659531}, {"id": 92952, "content": "钱难赚，房价tm的去死！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 633062}, {"id": 93208, "content": "没钱吃东西还担心自己长胖", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 607950}, {"id": 92953, "content": "钱都还没借到，已经盘算好钱到了该怎么花", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 657551}, {"id": 92954, "content": "做一家赚钱的公司，更要做一家不止赚钱的公司", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 657752}, {"id": 93211, "content": "生男孩还是女孩， 我还没有女朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 210724}, {"id": 93212, "content": "减肥之后就能找到男盆友", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 658387}]}